Nick Wechsler (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nick_Wechsler_(actor) 0 Samuel Nicholas Wechsler (born September 3, 1978), known as Nick Wechsler, is an American actor. He is known for his roles as Kyle Valenti on The WB teen drama series Roswell, and as Jack Porter on the ABC primetime soap opera Revenge.
